// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1910 — Mass File Rename (noescape)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4bd65db9-87ee-58da-bf81-e700b1441ce6

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
